adstage:table_column.name: results
adstage:table_column.title: Results
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Results shows how many times users took action on your ads, according to the ads objective.

adstage:table_column.name: cpr
adstage:table_column.title: Cost per Result
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
Cost per Result shows how many times users took action on your ads, according to the ads objective.

CPR is results divided by total cost.

adstage:table_column.name: clicks
adstage:table_column.title: Clicks
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Clicks show how many times your ads have been clicked.

adstage:table_column.name: impressions
adstage:table_column.title: Impressions
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Impressions show how many times your ads have been shown.

adstage:table_column.name: ctr
adstage:table_column.title: CTR
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
Clickthrough rate shows how often people who saw your ad ended up clicking it.

CTR is clicks divided by impressions.

To improve your CTR, check out our 5 tips for creating effective ads.

adstage:table_column.name: spend
adstage:table_column.title: Spend
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Spend shows the amount you've been charged for your ads.

adstage:table_column.name: cpm
adstage:table_column.title: Average CPM
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
Average cost-per-thousand impressions shows the average amount that you've been charged for every thousand times your ads have been shown.

Average CPM is cost divided by impressions divided by 1,000.

adstage:table_column.name: cpc
adstage:table_column.title: Average CPC
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
Average cost-per-click shows the average amount that you've been charged for a click on your ads.

Average CPC is spend divided by clicks.

adstage:table_column.name: conversions
adstage:table_column.title: Website Conversions
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
Website Conversions show how many times a click on your ad resulted in a meaningful action like a sale, lead or sign-up.

Conversion goals can be created and managed in the goals page.

adstage:table_column.name: conversion_rate
adstage:table_column.title: Conversion Rate
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
Conversion rate shows how often a click on your ad resulted in a conversion.

Conversion rate is conversions divided by clicks.

adstage:table_column.name: cpa
adstage:table_column.title: Cost per Conversion
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
Cost-per-conversion (also known as cost-per-acquisition) shows the average amount a conversion has cost you.

Cost-per-conversion is conversions divided by spend.

adstage:table_column.name: goal:*:conversions_many_per_click
adstage:table_column.title: AdStage Conversions
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
AdStage Conversions show how many times a click on your ad resulted in a meaningful action like a sale, lead or sign-up.

Conversion goals can be created and managed in the goals page.

adstage:table_column.name: goal:*:conversion_rate_many_per_click
adstage:table_column.title: AdStage Conversion Rate
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
AdStage conversion rate shows how often a click on your ad resulted in a conversion.

Conversion rate is conversions divided by clicks.

adstage:table_column.name: goal:*:cpa_many_per_click
adstage:table_column.title: AdStage Cost per Conversion
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
AdStage Cost-per-conversion (also known as cost-per-acquisition) shows the average amount a conversion has cost you.

Cost-per-conversion is conversions divided by spend.

adstage:table_column.name: engagements
adstage:table_column.title: Engagements
adstage:table_column.tooltip:
Enagements shows all clicks on the ad including retweets, replies, favorites and follows.
This includes clicks you are not billed for.

adstage:table_column.name: cpe
adstage:table_column.title: Cost Per Engagement
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Cost Per Engagement is the average cost for each engagement on a campaign.

adstage:table_column.name: follows
adstage:table_column.title: Followers
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Followers shows the number of times a user followed your account as a result of your ad.

adstage:table_column.name: replies
adstage:table_column.title: Replies
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Replies shows the number of times a user replied as a result of your ad.

adstage:table_column.name: retweets
adstage:table_column.title: Retweets
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Retweets shows the number of times your tweet was reposted or shared by a user.

adstage:table_column.name: link_clicks
adstage:table_column.title: Link Clicks
adstage:table_column.tooltip: Link clicks show the number of clicks on external links appearing in your ad.

adstage:table_column.name: video_views
adstage:table_column.title: Video Views
adstage:table_column.tooltip: The number of times your video was viewed for 3 seconds or more.
